      "content": "it's just hard to believe in a \"path forward\" when there isn't even anything left to move toward. my advisor basically told me my work isn't viable anymore. my funding is gone. it's like my whole identity was this researcher and now i'm just... nothing. it feels like i've been running a marathon for years and i've finally hit a wall i can't get over. there's no more energy left to even fight it.",
