      "content": "i know people say \"worth isn't tied to work\" but that feels like such a hollow platitude right now. it's not just about the job, it's the feeling that i've failed at the one thing i was supposed to do. everything is just so loud and heavy all the time. even being \"a person\" feels like too much effort. i just keep thinking about how much easier it would be if i didn't have to wake up and face this version of my life every single morning. if i could just... opt out of the struggle entirely.",
